trans-unit.source: Library to interact with a PD9530 handheld scanner
trans-unit.target: 图书馆与PD9530手持式扫描仪进行交互。

trans-unit.source: Library to use Datalogic(r) PowerScan(r) PD-9530 with USB-COM or RS232 on Windows(r) and UNIXes
PowerScan and DataLogic are registered trademarks of Datalogic ADC. in many countries, including the U.S.A. and the E.U. Windows is a registered trademark by Microsoft Corporation
trans-unit.target: PowerScan和DataLogic是Datalogic ADC.在许多国家(包括美国和欧盟)的注册商标,Windows是微软公司的注册商标。

trans-unit.source: The package depends on pySerial for communication and pywin32 for sending keystrokes.
trans-unit.target: 该包依赖pySerial进行通信,依赖pywin32发送按键。
